'''FM Sunrise Pakistan''' is a [[FM broadcasting|FM]] [[Radio Station]] in [[Pakistan]]. It is broadcast from [[Jhelum]], [[Islamabad]], [[Sargodha]] and [[Sahiwal]]. Radio FM Sunrise Pakistan serves the area with a motto "'''''Love People Love Pakistan'''''", so it designs and produces various programs to highlight the developmental projects with interaction of the masses. Different segments for particular groups of listeners are planned for youth, children, women and Armed Forces.
